steps {
  type: CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_USER_INPUT
  status: CORTEX_STEP_STATUS_DONE
  metadata {
    created_at {
      seconds: 1784484804
      nanos: 9495521
    }
    source: CORTEX_STEP_SOURCE_USER_EXPLICIT
  }
  user_input {
    user_response: "Create a modern, fun, mobile-first landing page for a new mobile application called \"Beyond Hello\".\n\nBrand:\nBeyond Hello\n\nHeadline:\n\"A social experience platform for singles\"\n\nCore idea:\nBeyond Hello is a new mobile app that helps singles meet through fun real-world experiences and challenges instead of endless swiping and boring chats.\n\nThis is NOT a traditional dating app.\nIt is a mobile social experience app where people connect by doing things together.\n\nThe goal:\nCreate excitement, curiosity, and a feeling of:\n\"I want to download this when it launches.\"\n\nTarget audience:\nSingles aged 25-45 in Prague.\nYoung professionals, expats, creatives, and socially active people.\nPeople who want meaningful connections but are tired of traditional dating apps.\n\nBrand personality:\n- Fun\n- Optimistic\n- Playful\n- Human\n- Modern\n- Inclusive\n- Adventurous\n- Community-driven\n\nAvoid:\n- Traditional dating app visuals\n- Red hearts\n- Romantic clich\303\251s\n- Luxury/corporate feeling\n- Serious business startup aesthetics\n- Generic stock photos\n\nVisual style:\nCreate a vibrant modern mobile app startup aesthetic.\n\nInspiration:\n- Airbnb Experiences\n- Duolingo\n- Headspace\n- Spotify\n- Modern Gen Z / millennial social apps\n\nDesign:\n- Bright but elegant colors\n- Rounded cards\n- Playful animations\n- Friendly typography\n- Large app screenshots\n- Mobile phone mockups\n- Interactive feeling\n\nColor direction:\nUse:\n- warm backgrounds\n- energetic accent colors\n- gradients\n- playful illustrations\n- modern UI cards\n\nThe website should immediately communicate:\n\"This is a mobile app.\"\n\n---\n\nPAGE STRUCTURE:\n\nSECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO\n\nShow a large smartphone mockup displaying the Beyond Hello mobile application.\n\nInside the phone:\nShow example app screens:\n- user profile\n- upcoming challenge\n- experience invitation\n- match notification\n- event discovery\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Beyond Hello\"\n\n\"A social experience platform for singles\"\n\nSupporting text:\n\n\"Meet people differently. Discover Prague through challenges, experiences, and moments that create real connections.\"\n\nPrimary CTA:\n\"Join the Prague launch\"\n\nSecondary CTA:\n\"Download app when available\"\n\nAdd:\n\"Coming soon to iOS and Android\"\n\nInclude App Store and Google Play style badges as \"Coming Soon\".\n\n---\n\nSECTION 2 \342\200\224 The Problem\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Dating apps created more matches. Not more connections.\"\n\nShow playful illustrations:\n\n\342\235\214 Endless swiping\n\342\235\214 Endless small talk\n\342\235\214 Forgettable first dates\n\nThen:\n\n\342\234\205 Real experiences\n\342\234\205 Better conversations\n\342\234\205 Memorable moments\n\n---\n\nSECTION 3 \342\200\224 How the app works\n\nCreate a visual 4-step mobile journey:\n\n1.\nCreate your profile\n\n2.\nDiscover challenges and experiences\n\n3.\nMeet interesting singles in Prague\n\n4.\nBuild real connections\n\nUse phone screenshots and animated transitions.\n\n---\n\nSECTION 4 \342\200\224 Experience Challenges\n\nShow colorful challenge cards:\n\nExample:\n\n\342\230\225 Coffee Quest\n\"Find Prague\'s most interesting caf\303\251 together\"\n\n\360\237\223\270 City Explorer\n\"Complete a photo challenge around Prague\"\n\n\360\237\215\234 Taste Adventure\n\"Discover a new restaurant\"\n\n\360\237\216\262 Conversation Challenge\n\"Answer questions you would never normally ask\"\n\nMake this section feel fun and shareable.\n\n---\n\nSECTION 5 \342\200\224 Why Beyond Hello\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Because meeting people should be an experience.\"\n\nFeature cards:\n\n\360\237\214\215 Discover your city\nExplore Prague in a new way\n\n\342\234\250 More than a profile\nConnect through personality and experiences\n\n\360\237\244\235 Less pressure\nNo awkward interview-style dates\n\n\360\237\216\211 More stories\nEvery connection starts with something memorable\n\n---\n\nSECTION 6 \342\200\224 Built for Prague\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Launching first in Prague\"\n\nShow:\n- Prague streets\n- caf\303\251s\n- parks\n- cultural places\n- social events\n\nText:\n\n\"Prague is full of amazing places and interesting people. Beyond Hello brings them together.\"\n\n---\n\nSECTION 7 \342\200\224 Join the first community\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Be one of the first 1,000 members\"\n\nCreate urgency:\n\n\"Help shape the future of social connection in Prague.\"\n\nSignup form:\n- Name\n- Email\n- Age range\n- Gender\n- What are you looking for?\n\nCTA:\n\"Reserve my place\"\n\n---\n\nSECTION 8 \342\200\224 Mobile App Preview\n\nCreate a final section showing:\n\n\"Your next connection starts with an experience.\"\n\nShow multiple phone screens:\n- Home feed\n- Challenge screen\n- Match screen\n- Profile screen\n- Event screen\n\n---\n\nTechnical requirements:\n\n- Build as a responsive React/Tailwind landing page\n- Mobile-first design\n- Include smooth animations\n- Modern app startup quality\n- Use realistic mobile app mockups\n- Make it feel like a real product launching in Prague\n- Optimize for email signups\n- Premium but playful\n- The final design should look like a funded startup preparing for launch\n"
    items {
      text: "Create a modern, fun, mobile-first landing page for a new mobile application called \"Beyond Hello\".\n\nBrand:\nBeyond Hello\n\nHeadline:\n\"A social experience platform for singles\"\n\nCore idea:\nBeyond Hello is a new mobile app that helps singles meet through fun real-world experiences and challenges instead of endless swiping and boring chats.\n\nThis is NOT a traditional dating app.\nIt is a mobile social experience app where people connect by doing things together.\n\nThe goal:\nCreate excitement, curiosity, and a feeling of:\n\"I want to download this when it launches.\"\n\nTarget audience:\nSingles aged 25-45 in Prague.\nYoung professionals, expats, creatives, and socially active people.\nPeople who want meaningful connections but are tired of traditional dating apps.\n\nBrand personality:\n- Fun\n- Optimistic\n- Playful\n- Human\n- Modern\n- Inclusive\n- Adventurous\n- Community-driven\n\nAvoid:\n- Traditional dating app visuals\n- Red hearts\n- Romantic clich\303\251s\n- Luxury/corporate feeling\n- Serious business startup aesthetics\n- Generic stock photos\n\nVisual style:\nCreate a vibrant modern mobile app startup aesthetic.\n\nInspiration:\n- Airbnb Experiences\n- Duolingo\n- Headspace\n- Spotify\n- Modern Gen Z / millennial social apps\n\nDesign:\n- Bright but elegant colors\n- Rounded cards\n- Playful animations\n- Friendly typography\n- Large app screenshots\n- Mobile phone mockups\n- Interactive feeling\n\nColor direction:\nUse:\n- warm backgrounds\n- energetic accent colors\n- gradients\n- playful illustrations\n- modern UI cards\n\nThe website should immediately communicate:\n\"This is a mobile app.\"\n\n---\n\nPAGE STRUCTURE:\n\nSECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO\n\nShow a large smartphone mockup displaying the Beyond Hello mobile application.\n\nInside the phone:\nShow example app screens:\n- user profile\n- upcoming challenge\n- experience invitation\n- match notification\n- event discovery\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Beyond Hello\"\n\n\"A social experience platform for singles\"\n\nSupporting text:\n\n\"Meet people differently. Discover Prague through challenges, experiences, and moments that create real connections.\"\n\nPrimary CTA:\n\"Join the Prague launch\"\n\nSecondary CTA:\n\"Download app when available\"\n\nAdd:\n\"Coming soon to iOS and Android\"\n\nInclude App Store and Google Play style badges as \"Coming Soon\".\n\n---\n\nSECTION 2 \342\200\224 The Problem\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Dating apps created more matches. Not more connections.\"\n\nShow playful illustrations:\n\n\342\235\214 Endless swiping\n\342\235\214 Endless small talk\n\342\235\214 Forgettable first dates\n\nThen:\n\n\342\234\205 Real experiences\n\342\234\205 Better conversations\n\342\234\205 Memorable moments\n\n---\n\nSECTION 3 \342\200\224 How the app works\n\nCreate a visual 4-step mobile journey:\n\n1.\nCreate your profile\n\n2.\nDiscover challenges and experiences\n\n3.\nMeet interesting singles in Prague\n\n4.\nBuild real connections\n\nUse phone screenshots and animated transitions.\n\n---\n\nSECTION 4 \342\200\224 Experience Challenges\n\nShow colorful challenge cards:\n\nExample:\n\n\342\230\225 Coffee Quest\n\"Find Prague\'s most interesting caf\303\251 together\"\n\n\360\237\223\270 City Explorer\n\"Complete a photo challenge around Prague\"\n\n\360\237\215\234 Taste Adventure\n\"Discover a new restaurant\"\n\n\360\237\216\262 Conversation Challenge\n\"Answer questions you would never normally ask\"\n\nMake this section feel fun and shareable.\n\n---\n\nSECTION 5 \342\200\224 Why Beyond Hello\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Because meeting people should be an experience.\"\n\nFeature cards:\n\n\360\237\214\215 Discover your city\nExplore Prague in a new way\n\n\342\234\250 More than a profile\nConnect through personality and experiences\n\n\360\237\244\235 Less pressure\nNo awkward interview-style dates\n\n\360\237\216\211 More stories\nEvery connection starts with something memorable\n\n---\n\nSECTION 6 \342\200\224 Built for Prague\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Launching first in Prague\"\n\nShow:\n- Prague streets\n- caf\303\251s\n- parks\n- cultural places\n- social events\n\nText:\n\n\"Prague is full of amazing places and interesting people. Beyond Hello brings them together.\"\n\n---\n\nSECTION 7 \342\200\224 Join the first community\n\nHeadline:\n\n\"Be one of the first 1,000 members\"\n\nCreate urgency:\n\n\"Help shape the future of social connection in Prague.\"\n\nSignup form:\n- Name\n- Email\n- Age range\n- Gender\n- What are you looking for?\n\nCTA:\n\"Reserve my place\"\n\n---\n\nSECTION 8 \342\200\224 Mobile App Preview\n\nCreate a final section showing:\n\n\"Your next connection starts with an experience.\"\n\nShow multiple phone screens:\n- Home feed\n- Challenge screen\n- Match screen\n- Profile screen\n- Event screen\n\n---\n\nTechnical requirements:\n\n- Build as a responsive React/Tailwind landing page\n- Mobile-first design\n- Include smooth animations\n- Modern app startup quality\n- Use realistic mobile app mockups\n- Make it feel like a real product launching in Prague\n- Optimize for email signups\n- Premium but playful\n- The final design should look like a funded startup preparing for launch\n"
    }
  }
