    thinking: "**Considering Firebase Integration**\n\nI\'m evaluating the need for Firebase integration for \"Beyond Hello.\" The landing page will require user signups, and durable cloud persistence is a potential requirement. I\'m focusing on whether Firebase is the appropriate solution for handling user data effectively. I will wait and see if it\'s needed.\n\n\n**Prioritizing User Data Security**\n\nI\'m now prioritizing data security for the landing page. Given the focus on email signups, local storage might suffice initially. I\'m leaning toward using local storage or a mock database, but can easily implement an exportable stats dashboard. I\'ll only consider a cloud database, like Firestore, if the user explicitly needs durable persistence or demands cloud-based storage.\n\n\n"
