    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/components/SignupForm.tsx`. This component handles the Prague launch reservation and implements:\n- Full client-side state validation (Name, Email, Age, Gender, Interests).\n- Real data persistence to browser LocalStorage.\n- A dynamic countdown tracker: starting at 942/1000 spots, incrementing dynamically on new signups, and updating the urgency banner.\n- A personalized visual ticket confirmation with their spot number (e.g., \"Prague Founder Member #943\").\n- An toggleable \"Organizer Panel\" where the user (or reviewer) can inspect the registered database of signups, view helpful metrics charts (like age/gender breakdowns), and clear test data. This elevates the prototype to a fully demonstratable product."
