n></select><button class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-900 text-white py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold tracking-tight shadow-xl\\\">Reserve my place</button></form><div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\"><span class=\\\"w-8 h-px bg-slate-200\\\"></span><span>Be adventurous</span><span class=\\\"w-8 h-px bg-slate-200\\\"></span></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-[#F5F1FF] p-5 rounded-3xl space-y-2\\\"><span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\342\234\250</span><h4 class=\\\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\\\">More than a profile</h4><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Connect through personality and shared action.</p></div><div class=\\\"bg-[#EBF7FF] p-5 rounded-3xl space-y-2\\\"><span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\360\237\214\215</span><h4 class=\\\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\\\">Discover Prague</h4><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Explore hidden spots in the city you love.</p></div></div></div></main><footer class=\\\"px-12 py-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-md border-t border-white/50\\\"><div class=\\\"flex space-x-8 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400\\\"><span>How it works</span><span>Challenges</span><span>Safety</span><span>Privacy</span></div><div class=\\\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400\\\">\302\251 2024 Beyond Hello. Built with \342\235\244\357\270\217 for Prague.</div></footer></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
